data.description: Here's the home that you've been waiting for! Right in the heart of highly sought after Union Valley, this home has it all! Country living while also minutes away from shopping and restaurants. From the open concept living room, 10ft ceilings throughout the home, fully functioning security system, lots of natural light, and a gated neighborhood, to an oasis right in your backyard. In 2023, the pool and fence were added. The black pipe fence completes the acre and a half lot and the pool has a 7ft tanning ledge and goes to 9ft deep. The yard was fully seeded and will have Bermuda growing in the Spring. The home features full gas appliances, tankless water heater, gas fireplace, stainless steel appliances, large kitchen island, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, formal dining room, breakfast nook and an office. Located 20 minutes east of Rockwall with lots of shopping and restaurant's nearby, and only 36 miles from downtown Dallas.
